codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. \'Lauda|nd|us -a -um\' est ~, quod est adiectīvum prīmae et secundae dēclīnātiōnis. Choose from this set of possible answers [ gerundīvum, ndus ndus endus endus, enda est] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-curie-001' where ANSWER in [ 'gerundīvum', 'ndus ndus endus endus', 'enda est']
